org.batfish.symbolic

Class AstVisitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.batfish.symbolic.AstVisitor

  • public class AstVisitor
extends java.lang.Object
    A helper visitor class for the Batfish datamodel. The AstVisitor lets users walk over each statement and expression in the Batfish datamodel and apply callback functions on the element.
